                        <div class="faq__item">
                            <div class="faq__item-wrapper">
                                <div class="faq__item-question">
                                    <div class="faq__item-question-text">What is KYC and eKYC?</div>
                                    <div class="faq__item-question-icon">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                                            <path d="M15.3312 6.71213C15.5193 6.45753 15.8732 6.38147 16.1515 6.54612C16.4485 6.72192 16.5469 7.10523 16.3712 7.40224V7.40305H16.3704V7.40386C16.3699 7.40477 16.3689 7.40634 16.368 7.40793C16.3661 7.41115 16.3634 7.41586 16.3598 7.42177C16.3527 7.43363 16.3423 7.4509 16.3289 7.47304C16.3019 7.51765 16.2618 7.58241 16.2109 7.66428C16.1092 7.82798 15.962 8.06088 15.778 8.33974C15.4106 8.89632 14.8939 9.64169 14.2985 10.3897C13.7059 11.1342 13.0199 11.901 12.3144 12.4869C11.6329 13.0529 10.8251 13.5424 9.99998 13.5424C9.17501 13.5424 8.36706 13.0529 7.68553 12.4869C6.98015 11.901 6.29495 11.1342 5.70229 10.3897C5.10675 9.64159 4.58944 8.89638 4.22199 8.33974C4.03792 8.06089 3.89074 7.82797 3.78905 7.66428C3.7382 7.58244 3.69806 7.51763 3.67105 7.47304C3.65766 7.45093 3.64722 7.43362 3.64012 7.42177C3.6366 7.41588 3.63389 7.41114 3.63198 7.40793C3.63105 7.40637 3.63007 7.40476 3.62954 7.40386V7.40305H3.62873V7.40224C3.45305 7.10526 3.55152 6.72194 3.84845 6.54612C4.12678 6.38148 4.48066 6.45752 4.66877 6.71213L4.7062 6.76829C4.7076 6.77064 4.7097 6.77466 4.71271 6.77968C4.71879 6.78982 4.72801 6.80565 4.74038 6.82607C4.76512 6.8669 4.80207 6.92756 4.85024 7.0051C4.94674 7.16042 5.08836 7.38325 5.26528 7.65126C5.61982 8.18833 6.11516 8.90157 6.68049 9.61171C7.24861 10.3253 7.87263 11.0172 8.48387 11.525C9.11912 12.0526 9.63543 12.2924 9.99998 12.2924C10.3648 12.2924 10.8809 12.0526 11.5161 11.525C12.1275 11.0171 12.7521 10.3255 13.3203 9.61171C13.8856 8.90159 14.3802 8.18833 14.7347 7.65126C14.9116 7.38324 15.0532 7.16042 15.1497 7.0051C15.1979 6.92754 15.2349 6.8669 15.2596 6.82607C15.272 6.80565 15.2812 6.78982 15.2873 6.77968C15.2902 6.77468 15.2924 6.77063 15.2938 6.76829L15.3312 6.71213Z" fill="#FBFBFB"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="faq__item-answer">
                                    <div class="faq__item-answer-text">
                                        <p>KYC stands for "Know Your Customer" — a mandatory identity verification process required by financial regulators worldwide to prevent money laundering, fraud, and terrorist financing. It's the cornerstone of trust between businesses and their customers, ensuring that people are who they claim to be. Traditional KYC often involves physical document submission and in-person verification, which can take days or even weeks.</p>
                                        <p>eKYC, or electronic KYC, transforms this process entirely. Using digital solutions like our platform, the entire verification happens online within minutes. Customers simply upload their documents and take a selfie from anywhere in the world. Our technology handles the rest — verifying document authenticity, matching faces, and running compliance checks. The result? The same regulatory compliance and security, but with a seamless experience that keeps your customers happy and your business moving forward.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="faq__item">
                            <div class="faq__item-wrapper">
                                <div class="faq__item-question">
                                    <div class="faq__item-question-text"> Which documents and countries does our solution support?</div>
                                    <div class="faq__item-question-icon">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                                            <path d="M15.3312 6.71213C15.5193 6.45753 15.8732 6.38147 16.1515 6.54612C16.4485 6.72192 16.5469 7.10523 16.3712 7.40224V7.40305H16.3704V7.40386C16.3699 7.40477 16.3689 7.40634 16.368 7.40793C16.3661 7.41115 16.3634 7.41586 16.3598 7.42177C16.3527 7.43363 16.3423 7.4509 16.3289 7.47304C16.3019 7.51765 16.2618 7.58241 16.2109 7.66428C16.1092 7.82798 15.962 8.06088 15.778 8.33974C15.4106 8.89632 14.8939 9.64169 14.2985 10.3897C13.7059 11.1342 13.0199 11.901 12.3144 12.4869C11.6329 13.0529 10.8251 13.5424 9.99998 13.5424C9.17501 13.5424 8.36706 13.0529 7.68553 12.4869C6.98015 11.901 6.29495 11.1342 5.70229 10.3897C5.10675 9.64159 4.58944 8.89638 4.22199 8.33974C4.03792 8.06089 3.89074 7.82797 3.78905 7.66428C3.7382 7.58244 3.69806 7.51763 3.67105 7.47304C3.65766 7.45093 3.64722 7.43362 3.64012 7.42177C3.6366 7.41588 3.63389 7.41114 3.63198 7.40793C3.63105 7.40637 3.63007 7.40476 3.62954 7.40386V7.40305H3.62873V7.40224C3.45305 7.10526 3.55152 6.72194 3.84845 6.54612C4.12678 6.38148 4.48066 6.45752 4.66877 6.71213L4.7062 6.76829C4.7076 6.77064 4.7097 6.77466 4.71271 6.77968C4.71879 6.78982 4.72801 6.80565 4.74038 6.82607C4.76512 6.8669 4.80207 6.92756 4.85024 7.0051C4.94674 7.16042 5.08836 7.38325 5.26528 7.65126C5.61982 8.18833 6.11516 8.90157 6.68049 9.61171C7.24861 10.3253 7.87263 11.0172 8.48387 11.525C9.11912 12.0526 9.63543 12.2924 9.99998 12.2924C10.3648 12.2924 10.8809 12.0526 11.5161 11.525C12.1275 11.0171 12.7521 10.3255 13.3203 9.61171C13.8856 8.90159 14.3802 8.18833 14.7347 7.65126C14.9116 7.38324 15.0532 7.16042 15.1497 7.0051C15.1979 6.92754 15.2349 6.8669 15.2596 6.82607C15.272 6.80565 15.2812 6.78982 15.2873 6.77968C15.2902 6.77468 15.2924 6.77063 15.2938 6.76829L15.3312 6.71213Z" fill="#FBFBFB"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="faq__item-answer">
                                    <div class="faq__item-answer-text">
                                        <p>We've built our platform to work globally. Our system recognizes and verifies over 10,000 types of government-issued documents from more than 200 countries and territories — from US driver's licenses and EU passports to national ID cards from emerging markets. Whether your customers use documents in Latin script, Cyrillic, Arabic, Chinese characters, or any other alphabet, our technology handles them all with equal precision.</p>
                                        <p>Beyond identity documents, we also verify proof of address through utility bills, bank statements, tax documents, and official government correspondence. This comprehensive coverage means you can onboard customers from virtually anywhere — whether they're in New York, Moscow, Dubai, or Tokyo — without worrying about document compatibility. Our global reach ensures your business can scale internationally without technical barriers.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="faq__item">
                            <div class="faq__item-wrapper">
                                <div class="faq__item-question">
                                    <div class="faq__item-question-text">How does this solution ensure compliance with regulations?</div>
                                    <div class="faq__item-question-icon">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                                            <path d="M15.3312 6.71213C15.5193 6.45753 15.8732 6.38147 16.1515 6.54612C16.4485 6.72192 16.5469 7.10523 16.3712 7.40224V7.40305H16.3704V7.40386C16.3699 7.40477 16.3689 7.40634 16.368 7.40793C16.3661 7.41115 16.3634 7.41586 16.3598 7.42177C16.3527 7.43363 16.3423 7.4509 16.3289 7.47304C16.3019 7.51765 16.2618 7.58241 16.2109 7.66428C16.1092 7.82798 15.962 8.06088 15.778 8.33974C15.4106 8.89632 14.8939 9.64169 14.2985 10.3897C13.7059 11.1342 13.0199 11.901 12.3144 12.4869C11.6329 13.0529 10.8251 13.5424 9.99998 13.5424C9.17501 13.5424 8.36706 13.0529 7.68553 12.4869C6.98015 11.901 6.29495 11.1342 5.70229 10.3897C5.10675 9.64159 4.58944 8.89638 4.22199 8.33974C4.03792 8.06089 3.89074 7.82797 3.78905 7.66428C3.7382 7.58244 3.69806 7.51763 3.67105 7.47304C3.65766 7.45093 3.64722 7.43362 3.64012 7.42177C3.6366 7.41588 3.63389 7.41114 3.63198 7.40793C3.63105 7.40637 3.63007 7.40476 3.62954 7.40386V7.40305H3.62873V7.40224C3.45305 7.10526 3.55152 6.72194 3.84845 6.54612C4.12678 6.38148 4.48066 6.45752 4.66877 6.71213L4.7062 6.76829C4.7076 6.77064 4.7097 6.77466 4.71271 6.77968C4.71879 6.78982 4.72801 6.80565 4.74038 6.82607C4.76512 6.8669 4.80207 6.92756 4.85024 7.0051C4.94674 7.16042 5.08836 7.38325 5.26528 7.65126C5.61982 8.18833 6.11516 8.90157 6.68049 9.61171C7.24861 10.3253 7.87263 11.0172 8.48387 11.525C9.11912 12.0526 9.63543 12.2924 9.99998 12.2924C10.3648 12.2924 10.8809 12.0526 11.5161 11.525C12.1275 11.0171 12.7521 10.3255 13.3203 9.61171C13.8856 8.90159 14.3802 8.18833 14.7347 7.65126C14.9116 7.38324 15.0532 7.16042 15.1497 7.0051C15.1979 6.92754 15.2349 6.8669 15.2596 6.82607C15.272 6.80565 15.2812 6.78982 15.2873 6.77968C15.2902 6.77468 15.2924 6.77063 15.2938 6.76829L15.3312 6.71213Z" fill="#FBFBFB"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="faq__item-answer">
                                    <div class="faq__item-answer-text">
                                        <p>Staying compliant shouldn't be a headache. Our platform continuously updates to meet evolving regulatory requirements across different jurisdictions. We maintain compliance with major frameworks including EU regulations (AMLD5/6, GDPR, eIDAS), US requirements (USA PATRIOT Act, FinCEN guidelines), and local regulations in markets worldwide. Our unique technology enables instant face comparison without storing or processing biometric templates, ensuring full GDPR compliance.</p>
                                        <p>What makes this practical for your business? You can configure different verification levels based on risk profiles and regional requirements. Need basic checks for low-value transactions? Done. Require enhanced due diligence for high-risk customers? We've got you covered. Every verification generates detailed audit trails and compliance reports, making regulatory reviews straightforward. Think of us as your compliance partner — we handle the complex regulatory landscape so you can focus on growing your business.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="faq__item">
                            <div class="faq__item-wrapper">
                                <div class="faq__item-question">
                                    <div class="faq__item-question-text">How does the system prevent fraud and verify the user is real?</div>
                                    <div class="faq__item-question-icon">
                                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none">
                                            <path d="M15.3312 6.71213C15.5193 6.45753 15.8732 6.38147 16.1515 6.54612C16.4485 6.72192 16.5469 7.10523 16.3712 7.40224V7.40305H16.3704V7.40386C16.3699 7.40477 16.3689 7.40634 16.368 7.40793C16.3661 7.41115 16.3634 7.41586 16.3598 7.42177C16.3527 7.43363 16.3423 7.4509 16.3289 7.47304C16.3019 7.51765 16.2618 7.58241 16.2109 7.66428C16.1092 7.82798 15.962 8.06088 15.778 8.33974C15.4106 8.89632 14.8939 9.64169 14.2985 10.3897C13.7059 11.1342 13.0199 11.901 12.3144 12.4869C11.6329 13.0529 10.8251 13.5424 9.99998 13.5424C9.17501 13.5424 8.36706 13.0529 7.68553 12.4869C6.98015 11.901 6.29495 11.1342 5.70229 10.3897C5.10675 9.64159 4.58944 8.89638 4.22199 8.33974C4.03792 8.06089 3.89074 7.82797 3.78905 7.66428C3.7382 7.58244 3.69806 7.51763 3.67105 7.47304C3.65766 7.45093 3.64722 7.43362 3.64012 7.42177C3.6366 7.41588 3.63389 7.41114 3.63198 7.40793C3.63105 7.40637 3.63007 7.40476 3.62954 7.40386V7.40305H3.62873V7.40224C3.45305 7.10526 3.55152 6.72194 3.84845 6.54612C4.12678 6.38148 4.48066 6.45752 4.66877 6.71213L4.7062 6.76829C4.7076 6.77064 4.7097 6.77466 4.71271 6.77968C4.71879 6.78982 4.72801 6.80565 4.74038 6.82607C4.76512 6.8669 4.80207 6.92756 4.85024 7.0051C4.94674 7.16042 5.08836 7.38325 5.26528 7.65126C5.61982 8.18833 6.11516 8.90157 6.68049 9.61171C7.24861 10.3253 7.87263 11.0172 8.48387 11.525C9.11912 12.0526 9.63543 12.2924 9.99998 12.2924C10.3648 12.2924 10.8809 12.0526 11.5161 11.525C12.1275 11.0171 12.7521 10.3255 13.3203 9.61171C13.8856 8.90159 14.3802 8.18833 14.7347 7.65126C14.9116 7.38324 15.0532 7.16042 15.1497 7.0051C15.1979 6.92754 15.2349 6.8669 15.2596 6.82607C15.272 6.80565 15.2812 6.78982 15.2873 6.77968C15.2902 6.77468 15.2924 6.77063 15.2938 6.76829L15.3312 6.71213Z" fill="#FBFBFB"/>
                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="faq__item-answer">
                                    <div class="faq__item-answer-text">
                                        <p>Real security comes from multiple layers of protection working together. Our platform starts by analyzing documents for signs of tampering, forgery, or digital manipulation — catching even sophisticated fakes that might fool the human eye. We then use advanced computer vision algorithms to match the face from the document with a live selfie, achieving 99.74% accuracy (NIST-verified). Our liveness detection goes further, identifying attempts to use photos, videos, masks, or deepfakes in real-time.</p>
                                        <p>But fraud prevention doesn't stop at onboarding. Our system can flag duplicate accounts by comparing new users against your existing database, detect suspicious patterns, and integrate with global watchlists for sanctions and PEP screening. The beauty is that legitimate customers experience a smooth, quick process — typically under 30 seconds — while fraudsters hit multiple roadblocks. It's like having a security expert who never sleeps, constantly protecting your business while keeping the customer experience frictionless.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

