                                        </svg>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="faq__item-answer">
                                    <div class="faq__item-answer-text">
                                        <p>Absolutely. We understand that when customers trust you with their identity documents, that trust is sacred. All data transmission uses bank-grade encryption, and stored information is protected with multiple security layers. We follow strict data minimization principles — we only process what's necessary for verification and don't retain data longer than required. Our facial analysis technology works without creating or storing biometric templates, using neural networks that simply determine if two faces match.</p>
                                        <p>Access to customer data is strictly controlled and monitored. We undergo regular security audits and penetration testing to ensure our defenses stay ahead of threats. Customers maintain control over their data — they can request deletion, and we provide clear transparency about how their information is used. We're fully compliant with GDPR and other privacy regulations, treating every piece of customer data with the respect and protection it deserves. Your customers' privacy isn't just a feature — it's fundamental to how we've built our entire platform.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

